Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:05.65,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Passione is a major organization \N comprised of gangsters.{"organization comprised of gangsters" sounds really clunky to me. "gangster organization"? -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:11.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,At the lowest rank are groups \N containing six to ten members, such as my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.91,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Capos like Polpo command those teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:17.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They take control of specific areas,\N making them their turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:22.41,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,There are also certain specialized teams,\N such as the assassination team and drug team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:27.59,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Even though we're part of the same organization,\N I prefer not to associate with those teams or their capos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.38,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The boss towers above the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:34.55,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The only person he trusts enough to \N contact directly is his right hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:38.72,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We have no way of finding out \N who he is or where he's hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:43.56,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Gangsters in this country hate standing out, \N since it makes them a target for assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:51.40,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So even capos dress normally to blend into crowds,\N and some even have cover jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:55.86,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,This is especially true of the boss.\N He won't reveal his identity to anyone. {Yup, looking back at this line after having seen the whole show... The "dress normally" statement is every bit as ludicrous for the boss as it is for anyone else. -Starfish} {It was a simpler time. -Axel}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.16,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Snoop around, and you're dead in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:01.04,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I've known several operatives caught doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:05.46,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So, Giorno, in order for you and I \N to get close to our mysterious boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.58,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...we need to earn recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:13.76,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,If we can't earn the trust of someone close to the boss \N and achieve recognition, we'll never defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.18,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So to start with, \N we'll need to gain better standing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.10,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...so that one of us can be promoted to capo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.51,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We can't do this alone, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:23.60,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,A team we can trust...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.98,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We'll need one in order to \N take down the boss.
