Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:03.49,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}The news of the incarcerated Polpo's death \N spread among the other capos in Passione.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.54,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Intelligence team is saying it was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.08,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That ain't his style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:12.29,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Polpo was locked up in a special cell.\N No way he was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.50,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You think he defied the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.26,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Ya don't get many capos \N as trustworthy as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.09,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's even harder to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.38,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:23.93,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah... The problem is who's replacing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.34,Secondary,Hot Background Chick,0,0,0,,How do I look? {like a background character BUUUUUUUURN}{stupid sexy low-detail background character}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:30.02,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,I just got word that all the capos are freaking the hell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.15,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Seems like Polpo offed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.57,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Hey, watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.52,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.57,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Suicide? That fatass?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.32,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going, for fuck's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.74,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,I dunno if that Polpo guy was \N depressed because he was so fat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:52.71,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...or if rotting in prison made him melancholic,\N but either way, he was a complete pussy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:56.63,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,He deep-throated a gun \N and blew his brains out. {This is pretty crass, but I kinda feel like it works for Sale, especially based on everything else he's said about Polpo -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.88,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,You sure it was suicide \N and not murder or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:03.38,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Gotta be suicide. \N They did some autopsy thing on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.43,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Specialists who do that can tell the \N difference between suicide and murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.72,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Hey, the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.90,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,So anyway, you hear the\N rumors about Polpo's fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.11,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.36,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Never heard about those rumors, just like \N I ain't never heard about where the edge of the universe is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:25.11,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Rumor has it he exchanged a chunk of his fortune for gold and jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.87,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...and hid them somewhere \N before he went to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.08,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,A big, fat, hidden fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:34.50,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,It's black money he couldn't keep in the bank \N that even the organization didn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:39.50,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,No one was dumb enough to \N go after it while Polpo was alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:43.84,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...but now that he's dead, \N his money's up for grabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.68,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Literally free money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.81,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,They say it's worth about five billion lire. {yes, the number's right this time: gojuuoku -JMFW}{Thy dilligence is appreciated. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.31,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Five {\i1}billion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.81,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,I'd be flying to Monaco or Japan with a girl on both arms\N if I had that kind of money! {fkn weab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.07,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Not me. I'd work my way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:04.86,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,If that money made me a capo, \N I'd get to taste even sweeter honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.95,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,But who knows where it's hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.28,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Nobody knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.83,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Yeah. And I'm just spitballing {Not a typo -J}here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:16.58,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...but it's hard to imagine such a major fatass like Polpo\N even walking by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:20.13,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,You really think he could hide \N five billion by himself? {Emphasis here on "COULD". Because, y'know, he would be unlikely to be able to personally hide shit when he couldn't walk. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.17,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,He had someone do it for him. {Full-on rewrite, yo! -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.47,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Someone tight-lipped. {Full-on rewrite, yo! -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.39,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Not sure if someone \N that tight-lipped even {\i1}exists{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.72,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...but Polpo sure liked Buccellati.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.89,Main,Mario,0,0,0,,Buccellati? \N He's one of the thugs outta Naples, ain't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:37.73,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Yeah. \N If he'd have anyone hide it, it'd be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:45.40,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Now that Polpo's dead, \N Buccellati will probably go for the five billion lire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.66,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Even Buccellati can't resist \N that kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.04,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Hey, Zucchero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.71,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Zucchero actually fucking ditched me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.42,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Did he swallow all that bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.63,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,If you're gonna follow Buccellati, watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.13,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Apparently he and his underlings are Stand users, too. {Removed line break to not overlap TS -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.14,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Hey, Fugo... {Hi, Go. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.18,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,It's pretty nice outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.89,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Would it hurt to skip studying for a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:20.73,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I'm just not feeling it today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.06,Main,Waiter,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you for waiting.\N Here's your strawberry cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.73,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Listen, Narancia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.73,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}Set it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.36,Main,Waiter,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.36,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You're a talented guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:32.83,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Not just anyone would seek help after\N failing to get a proper grade school education. {I feel like this line could emphasize a bit more that Narancia was personally willing to ADMIT that he failed grade school and ASKED for help. Yeah, "seek" does imply that, but I feel like it could come across stronger. -Starfish}{Maybe something to the effect of (and shorter than) "Not just anyone could own up to failing grade school and seek help with their education"? - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.87,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You already learned \N your multiplication tables!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.58,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You'll get it if you do like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.46,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I know you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.55,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Ready? \N What's six times five?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.09,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Six times five... Six and five...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.55,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Thirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.89,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Correct! \N I knew you had it in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.93,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You basically have it half-solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.48,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,So that's it! \N Six times five is thirty! Sweet! {oh god i'm dying}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.90,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.65,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What do you mean? \N It's just strawberry ca{\fscx300}-{\r} {fugo's cut off by mista, but only the last syllable -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.36,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,No shit it's strawberry cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:09.03,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It sure as hell ain't \N chocolate cake or cheesecake! {cheesecake is all one word, chocolate cake isn't, so you kinda have to have the repeated "cake"}{If you want to, I think you can get away with omitting "cake" after "chocolate". I don't think it's superior to what's already there, though. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.74,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But that's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.53,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,There's {\i1}four{\i0} slices of cake! {4}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.70,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,They trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.58,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,This again, Mista?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.87,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:22.08,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Choosing from four things is bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.71,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Choosing from five things is cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.09,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Choosing from three things is cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.97,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But choosing from four things \N means bad shit's about to go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:37.06,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, another kid adopted a kitten from \N a litter of four that was born in our neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:41.44,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...and he lost an eye \N after the thing scratched it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.73,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,He beat it to death right after, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.32,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Like I said, that's just an old wives' tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:54.03,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Logically speaking, someone {\i1}has{\i0} to pick from four slices \N if they're all taken one-by-one. {It might just be me, but I think this line's a little confusingly worded. I get the gist of what Fugo's trying to say from context, but I don't think the line's communicating it very clearly. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.03,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:57.74,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The restaurant should've thought of that \N and brought out three slices instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.50,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Talk about bad service!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.67,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Jeez... Don't eat it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.55,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But I want strawberry cake! {got a hunger so complicated}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.26,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.09,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I did it, Fugo! Well? {Suggesting something like "How is it?" in place of "Well". - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.51,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You're finished? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.60,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.97,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Did I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.90,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You fucking dipshit! \N Are you fucking kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.74,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to pound \N this shit into your thick fucking skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.82,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You braindead motherfucker! {Even though this was already discussed, I do think that "retard" is usable here. "fucktard" is too much and I think "motherfucker" just doesn't quite track with Fugo's rage, unless the point is that he's just kinda saying shit without too much thought. I won't object to "motherfucker" being kept, but I figured I'd share my thoughts. - Toa} {Merriam-Webster says it is "brain-dead," not "braindead." I'll let you guys decide, though I opt for "brain-dead." -Axel}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.87,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Damn... He's totally snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:42.08,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,{\an8}You just told me six times five is fucking thirty! \N How the fuck could the answer be less than that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:42.08,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey, Abbacchio... \N You gonna eat that piece of cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.46,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.13,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,You just call me a \N braindead motherfucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.00,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I wouldn't look down on people if I was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:54.05,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,You're dead... \N I'm gonna kill you, Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.05,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,{\an8}You piece of shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:57.09,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What the hell are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I heard you yelling from the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.43,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You're bothering the other customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.31,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I brought the new member\N we talked about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.69,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you. \N His name is Giorno Giovanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.45,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm Giorno Giovanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.16,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.04,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.13,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}I'm{\i0} sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.84,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Narancia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.88,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I'll try harder next time,\N so teach me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:36.84,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:41.60,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I made the call to bring him here,\N so show some respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.60,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mr. Buccellati...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:42.97,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.89,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.85,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Ah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:50.65,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I expect you all to give Giorno\N a proper welcome. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.65,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a minute, Giorno. {LET THE PISS BEGIN}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.86,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'd like you all to get \N acquainted while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.32,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.45,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Giorno, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.58,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.79,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Let's talk over tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.16,Main,Waiter,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mr. Buccellati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:07.79,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.25,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Buccellati here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.67,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.64,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.34,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:24.06,Main,Menini,0,0,0,,Buccellati! \N Buccellati, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.89,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Mrs. Menini!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.52,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:33.07,Main,Menini,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask of you. \N Could we speak outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.65,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.62,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Here, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.83,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.79,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:51.13,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Fifteen? \N Jeez, you're two years younger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.13,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Thank you for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.89,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:06.22,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You just finished thanking me for \N so generously pouring that cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.60,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Would be pretty rude \N to not drink something you said thanks for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.40,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Or is it too lukewarm for your tastes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:16.61,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Maybe he won't since he's \N not serious about joining us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.57,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.74,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.07,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,They graciously poured me a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.62,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,No freakin' way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.58,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What did you guys do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.17,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Sick! He actually drank it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.97,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,D-Dude, you're insane! \N Did you seriously drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.89,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,There's no way he actually did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.85,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,So how did you do it?\N Where is the tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.89,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Just tell {\i1}me{\i0} at the very least! Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.77,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Who's to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:55.11,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You're all keeping your \N abilities secret too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.49,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,He's a Stand user? {we go from bullshit gio to derp gio}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.20,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,As to where the liquid in my cup went...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:08.29,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,I changed one of my teeth into a jellyfish \N composed of 98% liquid, then had it suck it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.58,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Can your ability \N move things or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.58,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}Open your mouth!\N You don't got a hole in there, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.54,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did you seriously drink it for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.71,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is it your favorite drink or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.63,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you tell me what your abilities are, \N I may tell you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.54,Thoughts,Bruno,0,0,0,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:19.63,Thoughts,Bruno,0,0,0,,...but Giorno Giovanna seems to\N have a knack for winning people over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.55,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You're a cautious guy. \N I can respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:24.59,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Does Buccellati know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.68,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:32.48,Thoughts,Bruno,0,0,0,,They aren't quite ready to work as a team, \N but we have no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.52,Thoughts,Bruno,0,0,0,,This has to happen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.31,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Enough screwing around! \N We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.73,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.44,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Follow me and you'll find out. \N Now let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.74,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,Buccellati! \N How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.16,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.33,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.66,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop by my store sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.04,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.79,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,So what are we doing about the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.21,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We got a loaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:01.09,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,As I suspected, the people here \N completely trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.75,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Too bad a certain {\i1}someone{\i0} ruined the last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.80,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, I already told you I didn't do it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:09.22,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,Buccellati, this is a dear friend of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:13.48,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,She's being abused by her son\N and doesn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.52,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.44,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,I see. That's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.65,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll give him a stern talking-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.07,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,What's your son's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.94,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.49,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,He's usually such a sweet boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.99,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,But he recently got into drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:34.66,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,Buccellati, I've lived in this \N neighborhood for fifty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:38.08,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,But for some time now, \N I've felt uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.59,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,Who keeps selling these awful drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.96,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,I'm so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.59,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,Please. Will you protect us, Buccellati?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.76,Flashback,Menini,0,0,0,,You're going to stand up for us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.43,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Yeah... I'll make things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.56,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll sort it out, somehow...
Comment: 0,0:13:59.02,0:13:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,C {shifted FORWARD 47 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.82,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,When you said we were heading out,\N you meant going on a cruise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.99,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,That's tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.57,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Since when do we own a yacht?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:10.62,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We're renting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.28,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.87,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Just a rental, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.04,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey, Buccellati...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:19.21,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Whatever you do,\N {\i1}please{\i0} don't rent one with the number four on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.58,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It'll sink for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.05,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,This again... \N It wouldn't be floating right now if that were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.09,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.13,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,How about {\i1}you{\i0} take it for a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.89,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We'd like to rent a yacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:37.48,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Sure thing! \N Pick whichever one you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.85,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Anything but four!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:42.77,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Fine. \N We'll take the one on the far left, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:46.28,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Of course. I'll give you the key.{"I'll go grab..." seems a bit weird when the keys are hanging right behind him and all he does is turn around and take it. Though this exact phrasing is probably a bit stiff, too. -Starfish} {"I'll get the key"? -Axel}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.99,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm thinking we'll need it for three days.\N How much is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:53.74,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I could never \N take your money, Mr. Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.58,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Take her out as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.04,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.00,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Pops, ring me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.23,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,This feels amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.16,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey, Narancia... Hey! {i love how you can hear next ep's feature song through the headphones}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.37,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.37,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,So, uh, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:42.37,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,You bought some drinks, didn'tcha?\N Wanna sell me one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.84,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Huh? \N Every time you say that, you always stiff me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:49.97,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Give me a break!\N Gimme one! C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.38,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,You're hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.26,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Cola or Spalite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:57.68,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Cola...\N A-Actually, I'll take Spalite since it's colorless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:15:59.85,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.27,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Thanks, man! \N Mind holding my magazine for a sec? {Quoting a suggestion (off memory) from when Josh livestreamed editing this episode for the first time: "Thanks, my nigga! Hey, can you do me a solid and hold this shit for me for a New York minute?". - Toa}{Beautiful -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.27,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Thank you... and a-thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:18.29,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong with this thing?\NIt just died on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.50,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Why'd the music stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.83,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I just bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.46,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Dammit! \N He's got balls to sell me this piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.54,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,That geezer from the electronics store \N is gonna pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:27.54,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:33.93,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Buccellati, come on already! \N Tell us where this boat is going! {Suggesting to contract "boat" and "is" into "boat's". - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.06,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Fine. We should be far enough \N away from shore by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.73,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We're headed to Capri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.02,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Capri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.44,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I suppose we're not \N going there for sightseeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.02,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.36,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Then what are we doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:56.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,This morning, \N the capo Polpo committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.58,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What? Suicide?! \N Polpo did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.45,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.33,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.83,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter why he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:06.63,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Polpo did plenty of stuff \N that could get him killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:10.80,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,But what does that have to do \N with going to Capri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:14.01,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,While he was alive, \N Polpo possessed a secret fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's worth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:17.09,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...ten billion lire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.01,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,T-Ten billion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.64,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm the only person who knows its location.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.48,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I was the one who hid it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:27.81,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,His ten billion belongs to us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.94,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,With that kind of money, \N the position of capo will be ours for the taking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.11,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.41,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,He's definitely the kind of guy \N who goes for broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.91,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,He's gonna become a capo,\N just like I hoped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:44.96,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,He earned this chance by working hard\N and getting recognition from a capo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.33,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:50.46,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Seriously? This just took a \N sudden turn for the awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.34,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.92,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Where in Capri did you \N hide all that treasure, Buccellati? {trying to make him sound slightly childish}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.68,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I can't say just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Rumors of his hidden fortune are \N already circulating within the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:04.64,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We can't let anyone know \N until we've secured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.77,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,B-Buccellati...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Hey! Something's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.36,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What's going on, Narancia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.03,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.07,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What the hell are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.45,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,H-Hey, come look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.99,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Only his shoe is left...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.66,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hand it over, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.66,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I don't understand what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.13,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Where did Narancia go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.67,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You guys didn't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:38.05,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It looked like Narancia \N was pulled into the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.43,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.30,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,That's not even possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:44.68,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,He couldn't have tripped and fallen \N into the ocean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.52,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Narancia, where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.23,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey, Narancia! \N If you're just screwing around and hiding from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.40,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...then tell us where you are already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.49,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Narancia, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.49,Secondary,Giorno,0,0,0,,Narancia! Please answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:57.86,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Mista?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.32,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Mista?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.24,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Mista?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.16,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Where did you go, Mista?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.54,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,He couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.12,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Come on, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.08,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Why are you messing around at a time like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.30,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Fugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.13,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Hey, Fugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.63,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.68,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.89,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio, Giorno, \N we need to stay close together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.39,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.02,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Someone is hiding on the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,This is a Stand attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.52,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,But why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.81,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The money...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:40.49,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,My knowledge of the fortune's location must have gotten out, \N and now someone is trying to beat us to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.32,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They're probably from the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:48.37,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You think they've been following us \N in hiding since we set out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:49.83,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:54.29,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They probably got fed up with waiting for me \N to reveal the location of the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.21,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They plan to eliminate you guys, \N then make me cough up the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:02.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They can take their time, too, \N since we're stranded out in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.39,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You mean Narancia and \N the others are dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.93,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I didn't say that. {Alternately, "Not necessarily." -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.76,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,But ten billion lire is at stake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.85,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They would gladly kill another \N member of the organization for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.69,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,No, Narancia and the others are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.90,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(770,1045)}They're somewhere on this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.94,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,1045)}I don't know if our attacker\N plans to use them as hostages...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.45,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...but they're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:28.12,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Giorno Giovanna, \N what the hell makes you so sure of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:33.08,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I used my Stand to \N turn Narancia's shoe into a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.54,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,1045)}It's attempting to return to its owner, Narancia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:41.13,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(655,1045)}If Narancia were truly dead, it wouldn't \N be buzzing around in search of him. {should we split the line at the comma? -JMFW}{nope -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Can you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.51,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's alive... \N He's alive, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:49.01,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,1045)}The fly isn't going down into \N the cabin or inside the locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.02,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It just keeps moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:55.10,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It's buzzing around that area \N in search of Narancia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.73,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What the hell is his ability, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.52,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Be quiet and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:03.15,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Narancia is somewhere \N near the cabin's entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.70,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That much is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.87,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Yet for some reason, \N the fly is lost and can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.95,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I believe it's safe to assume\N we'll find the enemy wherever Narancia is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:19.17,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,1045)}Likewise, I can confidently say that \N the enemy isn't merely hiding behind an object.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.25,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.33,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,So if we don't first solve \N the mystery of the enemy's ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:26.05,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...we'll be killed if we get close to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.14,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:31.22,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,1045)}But the fact that their ability requires them \N to attack while hidden is a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.27,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It means that once we've solved the mystery,\N we can defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:38.98,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,If you use your Stand, Abbacchio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.61,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...you may be able to \N defeat someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.44,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:48.07,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,{\pos(820,1045)}Can your ability \N solve the mystery for us?{Through adding a line break, I have made it so this line doesn't need to be quite as far out towards the edge of the frame as before!! -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:51.83,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.08,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Hey, Abbacchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:58.17,Main,Bruno,0,280,0,,Don't get hung up on petty \N bullshit at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.67,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Petty bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.92,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.46,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,My safety's at risk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:09.93,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'm not just gonna reveal my Stand ability \N to a stranger I don't trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:11.56,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Buccellati...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:15.18,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I don't know what \N made you trust this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:18.27,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...but I don't consider him one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:21.61,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,If we can't solve the mystery of this enemy, \N we'll all be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:26.28,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That's just a baseless theory \N from an untrustworthy brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:29.61,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's just his panicked imagination. \N He didn't {\i1}see{\i0} anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:30.62,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.83,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The enemy is just hiding \N somewhere in the cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:38.08,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll find them and take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.42,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,If we get close without solving the mystery, \N we'll be killed for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:42.71,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:47.17,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You goddamned brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.76,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I, Giorno Giovanna, have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:54.47,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What are you on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:58.64,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You can solve the mystery, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:00.10,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.06,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.36,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:11.20,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,G-Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.54,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The enemy is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:17.25,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:18.66,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Giorno is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.46,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Abbacchio...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:26.42,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Giorno Giovanna... \N You're one crazy son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.26,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,{\an8}All this just to prove yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.26,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you?
